    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nUpdating plugins with `vim.pack.update` fails. I suspect that the problem is in older version of git installed on my machine. The version is 2.25.1. Looks like the minimal supported version is 2.13: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/8367340b051530e251781a6abaeb0c4d4a4fe623/runtime/lua/vim/pack.lua#L755.\nI think git requirements should be also clarified in docs.\n\n<img width=\"1470\" height=\"316\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/bb2edfa1-8952-460d-8960-995eeb92aaf0\" />\n\nDoesn't reproduce with the newest git 2.53.0.\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nUse `$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/$NVIM_APPNAME/init.lua` for reproduction:\n\n```lua\nvim.pack.add({\"https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig\"})\n```\n\n1. NVIM_APPNAME=nvim_repro nvim --clean\n2. install a plugin by confirming prompt `Y`\n3. close nvim `:q`\n4. navigate to plugin repo `cd ~/$XDG_DATA_HOME/$NVIM_APPNAME/site/pack/core/opt/nvim-lspconfig`\n5. reset commit to the older commit `git reset --hard HEAD~1`\n6. open nvim\n7. run `:=vim.pack.update()`\n8. close confirm buffer with `:w` and wait for update end\n9. you can run `:=vim.pack.update()` again and see update not applied\n10. open `$XDG_STATE_HOME/$NVIM_APPNAME/nvim_pack.log`\n\nThe following error is logged:\n```\n========== Update 2026-04-01 09:48:28 ==========\n# Error ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n## nvim-lspconfig\n\n /opt/nvim/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/pack.lua:245: usage: git stash list [<options>]\n     or: git stash show [<options>] [<stash>]\n     or: git stash drop [-q|--quiet] [<stash>]\n     or: git stash ( pop | apply ) [--index] [-q|--quiet] [<stash>]\n     or: git stash branch <branchname> [<stash>]\n     or: git stash clear\n     or: git stash [push [-p|--patch] [-k|--[no-]keep-index] [-q|--quiet]\n            [-u|--include-untracked] [-a|--all] [-m|--message <message>]\n            [--] [<pathspec>...]]\n     or: git stash save [-p|--patch] [-k|--[no-]keep-index] [-q|--quiet]\n            [-u|--include-untracked] [-a|--all] [<message>]\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPlugin updated to the latest commit, no new updates available on the next `vim.pack.update` run.\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nv0.12.0\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nUbuntu 20.04.6 LTS\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGhostty 1.3.1\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nfrom github v0.12 release page: https://github.com/neovim/neovim-releases/releases/tag/v0.12.0",
